To      biryu belldandy vorlin~
Subject Changed the way rom boots...~
Text
This should give us a little leeway as far as permissions for anime
are concerned.  The mud is now permissions rwsrws--- owned by
anime.anime, and the logs will be owned by anime.anime_www.
The "anime" users is in both groups, anime and anime_www.
The logs will be rwxr-x--- to anime.anime_www.  This means:
People in the anime group can all start the MUD, which will
now run as an anime.anime, not whoever starts it.
People in anime_www can read (but not alter) the logs.
People not in either anime_www or anime can't see anything.
(That part needs a few minutes more work. :P)
That should deal with any future permissions screws ahead of
time, I tried being very paranoid throughout.  I've still got
some residual perms garbage to pitch out though, which will happen
here in the next few minutes.

Anyone have any objections to this?

Suzuran Majere, Deliverywitch. :P

Oh, BTW, everyone with boxaccess so far is in anime group except
Folken, who is anime_www.
~
