Subject The growing trend of anti-social mudding..~
Text
Ok all..youve heard it before...Dont bug me..I am not gonna help you with
ANYTHING, I dont want to talk to you, I dont want to look at you,
I dont want to here from you, I dont want to know you are alive, ETC ETC ETC
Well..
Thats not what I am posting this note to say.
If you ahve questions..go ahead and ask me..I may be wrong most of
the time, but i am still willing to help unless something pressing
is going on. After all, I spend msot of my time hitting Dragon punch
8 times, hitting heal self, then hitting dragon punch 8 times, washing, rinsing, and repeating
Keep in mind I am not an overly jaded mudder with 30 or 40 alts
