Stamp   953104799
To      all~
Subject I'm leaving~
Text
Hello all.  For those of you who care, I'm leaving anime.  I'll come back
someday.  I hope I made enough of an impression for any of you to give a
damn I'm leaving.  I don't care if it's you love me leaving or hate
it, as long as it effects you in some way.
Oh, and some of you need to understand that I have a small disease
called "Mental masochism" as I entitled it.  I enjoy having a few people
hate me.  Which is why I bashed, harassed, and otherwise tormented
People at my descretion.
That, and since I have a social life (drink, screw, forget) outside of anime
I couldn't care less what some of you thought of me.  I just came here,
probably for the same reason the rest of you do.  Because of an addiction.
I have plenty of them.  In any case, I'll be back, gee, knowing me, in a
month or so.  Just don't set your watches to me, I could take a day or a
year.  My clock's broken.

Oh yeah.  One more thing.  (I'm treating this as my Springer final thought
cuz it's fitting) When I DO return, I will take you all hostage.  No one
will be safe.  My demands will be harsh and inconsiderate.  I will make
Holly my whore.  The Light will be my left and, and the Executioner of
Anime will be my right.  Tetsuo will be my eyes, and Satan will be my loins.
And a new order will be wrought, from the unholy ashes.  Forget all you hold
dear, for I shall rape you of it.

*coughs*   I mean, I'll be back.

`     -- `8S`7e`&i`8T`&z`7e`8r`7 
~
