Sender  Kakeru~
Date    Thu Mar 16 00:16:50 2000~
Stamp   953187410
To      all~
Subject `2S`@wa`2t T`@ea`2m`` (big note)~
Text
Due to so many people asking for help, I've decided to open a title helper
team, called Swat Team (we are accepting color suggestions :p).

`#Why?``
Because we need a motivation (or another) to help people :)
And for some RP purposes also.

`#What?``
The swat members will help who needs with some things.

`&What we'll -DO-:``
`@*`` rescue corpses;
`@*`` rescue equipment (if they're on the ground or if a mob picked it up);
`@*`` kill aggro mobs that are in your way (example, guardians from hell);
`@*`` summon people (generally if they're blind, plagued AND cursed, or if
``  they're after 7th circle in dante's, however we'll try to summon
``  everyone who needs);
`@*`` heal people if they're mortally wounded/stunned/invalidated/something,
``  or if they're plagued/cursed/blinded/whatever at the healer and don't
``  have money to heal;
`@*`` cure blindness/plague/poison/whatever if the rescuer have the properly
``  spell.

`&What we'll -`!NOT`&- do:``
`!*`` get equipment from mobs, unless they picked it up from the ground
``  and it was yours;
`!*`` help levelling;
`!*`` help `!PK`1ers`` in any way.

A rescue member will not be able to help you if he/she is fighting, with no
hp/mana/move or [`1A`!F`1K``]. We'll generally help people under level 70, but if you
lost your lvl 90 corpse we'll help you if we can.

To ask for a rescue, send a me a tell with the word `&"rescue! <message>"`` (no quotes
and signals, and yes, it's a trigger, for RP purposes only) and I'll try to reply
to you and help immediately. Input in the message why you want the rescue and where
you are, examples:
- "I lost my corpse in the guardians of hell", or
- "I need a summon, I'm cursed on dante's inferno".

I'll maintain some statistics for how many people were rescued in a day, week,
month and yadayaddayadda, and the most requested reasons for rescue, so we'll have
an almost-complete helping statistic. It's more one useless thing made by me :)

And I'll try to stay in the `#K`7a`8ns`7a`#s`` bar and `&*TRY*`` to do some RPing when I'm free.
As this rescue experience will require a little bit of RP from the agents, we'll
introduce ourselves in the RP world of AnimeMUD.

`#I want to join!``
Send a note to me with these data: `&char name ``(duh), `&sex``, `&class``, `&race`` and `&level``.
After sending it you don't need my confirmation to put in your title that you're
on the squad and helping people following these rules. Just adjust your title
and begin your work :)

When I receive your note I'll reply your position and color to use (the title is
customized for each one, but if you want to use your own, you can, but you must
specific your position). The cause I need the data is to control of who are in
the team.

Monks and clerics are very welcome, but the team is opened to every class/race.
We only do not accept PKers.

Fell free to ask or suggest something you want.

Kakeru `![`7R`&escue `7A`&gent `#- `&1`8st`!]``
P.S.: I hope all my english is correct :p
~
