Subject OK, I'm officially disgusted with the both of you.~
Text
It has come to my attention that one or the other of you was
lying to the rest of us about the future of the clan.  So I decided
to do a little reading about.  I do have access to logfiles, you know.
And in case you guys don't know, EVERY command is logged.  It's really
informative.  I just wish I hadn't read it now.

Not only do I see Renala blatantly contradicting herself to several
people on a couple points, but I see Schala planning to PK her on
and alt and laugh about it - And then she complains about Renala's
lack of loyalty.

Renala, I've said before that it takes a whole lot to make me dislike
someone.  But LYING TO ME is one surefire way to do it.  That's all
I'm going to say.  If I continue, I'll say something I'll regret.

As for Schala, she does have the valid points that you're almost
never on, and you're not even really interested in this clan anyway.
I really can't say a whole lot bad about you other than you were
really quick to brand Renala as a traitor and then plot to exact
revenge on her rather than try working it out.  For the record,
Usagi seems to have a real thing for having me lead.  I dunno why.
I doubt she'd have much trouble convincing Biryu to get it done.
While I don't quite know whether or not I'm leader material,
I'm quite certain that, at the moment, neither of you two
are.  Now, you can either get your collective acts together and
figure out just who's going to be in charge here, or I can OK
Usagi to make me ldr and that will be the end of it.  If neither
of you wants to lead, I have no real problems doing it myself.

My primary reason for not OKing Usagi a week ago when she asked me
was that I didn't want to hurt either of your feelings.  But the
behaviour exhibited by the both of you is just plain disgusting.
Either shape up and settle this mess, or I'll nicely remove it.
I'd hate to do this, but if you leave me no option, it surely beats
having the clan die.
Can't beleve this.  We have 3 active members and an inactive ldr,
and 2 of these are fighting?  And you talk about loyalty.  Loyalty
is helping set each other straight, not taking revenge when one of
us screws up.

OK, I'm done.  Now it's up to you two.  How things go after here
depends entirely on your actions.
~
