Subject Rp Background~
Text
You may be wondering where does Aylea come from ... who is she?
Well she is one of the last Saiyans to escape from the planet Vegeta before it exploded many years ago.
Her survival pod, brought to the Planet Jupiter over a thousand years ago, was meant as a device to seed her in destroying the inhabitants living there as she came of age.
However, the people there were kind despite Aylea's attitude toward others.  Even many years later, when she was reborn on Earth she constantly got into fights while growing up.
But the people on Jupiter were kind and showed her how she could channel all the negative feelings she had to defeating evil.  She became a warrior against the dark negaforce of the universe.
Her many long battles while alone on Jupiter were not unoticed by Queen Serenity of the Moon Kingdom.
One day Queen Serenity called upon Aylea, nicknamed Lita by the Jupiter inhabitants, to fight with the champions of the other planets.
She met the other Sailor Scouts who welcomed a new friend.
However, she had man
However, she had many difficulties adjusting at first.
Exposure to such dark energy, while in constant  battles against the negaforce brought out some of the evil deep within her
from birth as part of her Saiyan heritage.
Queen Serenity recognized Aylea's inner struggle, and used the silver crystal to heal all of her dark feelings, bringing about a warrior with a pure heart to fight the negaforce.
After losing the battle with Queen Beryl years later, she was reborn on Earth as Lita, her nickname, however her inner strength from her Saiyan heritage could not be ignored as she still got into many fights in school.
However, with all of her friends helping her, she channeled her power toward fighting evil instead of helping it along, as Queen Serenity had done for her many years before.
------------------------------------------------------------------------
