Stamp   953973257
To      all~
Subject misc.~
Text
I've been meaning to write this note since the note spam concerning 
Saiyans...Well,here goes:

`&*``  About all those people asking for super saiyans and stuff,it 
probably won't happen,and if it did it should be a pk race with chance
to transform like demons/espers...
`&*``  Lately almost everybody complains how hard it is to level past
level 73...Well,i'm level 73 and personally,i think the xp should stay 
as it is...Lately i've seen nore lvl 80s than ever before (heh,although
most of them are thives and mages with a certain spell group) and frankly
my only complaint is that there should just be more agents in sec9.
Don't forget that sec9 only recently was modified and personally i'm
surprised it happened (seems like Vorlin is having a positive effect
on other imms as well...).
Well,if you find leveling is too boring past level 73,you can always
autoquest or rp...You shouldn't be able to get to level 90 in even a 
month.
`&*``  Another recent complaint was that clan leaders are too hard to
kill.Think people,leaders are supposed to be hard to kill,unless the
other guy is a leader too,or a level 90.Maybe the imms should consider
giving the rest of the clan members a tweaked down version of the cskills,
nothing too powerful,just something usefull.Otherwise,what's the point
of joining a clan?Rp purposed?Maybe,but when cskills were back in,PK
was actually thriving.
`&*``  And here's an idea of my own for all those spellcasters complain
ing about how they waste all their mana on a single agent and stuff :
Why not introduce a lvl 70+ spell group called draining or something
like that? It would new spells like Osmose , Rasp and Drain (anyone
familiar with Final Fantasy should recognise them).Osmose would transfer
mana from the target to the caster,Rasp would damage mana points and
Drain would transfer hp from the target to the caster.And all spells
would require a small amount of mana...It shouldn't be to hard to code
either...

Does it make any sense to anyone other than me?
Zeb.

P.S.  Looking forward to note spam...gives me something to read when i'm bored.
P.S.S. Sorry about the bad formatting and grammar/syntax/spelling errors...I'm too bored to correct any of those...
~
