Stamp   954049482
To      Jurai Fenris~
Subject The Druadic Assassin~
Text

``     Damn it was cold, the night air burned my cheeks. It was winter, so
every flake of snow seemed like stinging hail. I stood up the mountian
with Cyrrus by my side. He was my companion on these dark excursions... a
wolf I had found as a puppy and raised. 
``     I saw the door open and a sliver of light pour through... I cracked my
knuckles. `6'`^Keep that shipment on schedual...`6'`` the shadowed figured shouted
back into the warehouse. He wrapped a scarf about his neck and trudged off
into the snow. `6'`^That's him?`6'`7 I pondered, `6'`^Well, off we go.`6'`` I said, slapping
my hip... Cyrrus hopping along behind me. We followed the man for quite a
while, until he turned down a dark alley... how `&i`7ron`&i`7c. `6'`^Its time`6'`` I whispered,
the wolf yipping in agreement. I stood, this time without being very stealthy
about it. `6'`^W...what? Who's there?`6'`7 he called into the darkness... I answered
with a rasp of flame.
``     His body lie there, charred in the soft white snow... I looked away.
He was a drug dealer, takeing his shipments from the slums of Shadowloo and
bringing them to Neo-Tokyo... children lived here. He was your average middle
class man, the one that hired me. His daughter had been kidnapped and killed
by the drugdealers it seems... the police wouldn't do anything, so he came
to me... why did I take the job? Money? No... the self enjoyment? God no..
I did it because its all I know, as sad as that is....

Kaediin `&-`7 Level 82, `^E`6sper `$M`4age `8(`!PK`1set`8)``
H`&i`7tpo`&i`7nts: Enough `8- `7M`&a`7na: 2090 `8- `7Mov`&e`7me`&n`7t: 796``

"Hey, You're PK!" I know I know... hear me out. I talked it over with Fenris
and he said he's personally liked the idea of an 'assassin' among the Jurai
breathren. I know some of you RP your characters somewhat of that nature,
but the fact that you can't actually attack someone else stops your RP short,
that's where I come in =). But no, I'm not just some schmoe PK'r that wants
in Jurai.. I'm an Avid RPer as well. I roleplay my character as a Druid.. a
master of nature, animals and all. But on top of that I'm an assassin, which
makes for nice conflicting storylines for me to work with. 
Anyways... I am quite serious about joining your ranks, and I hope you take
my application with a little seriousness. I thank you for your Time ^_^.

Kaediin - Druid Circle

~
