Subject Sai-jins~
Text

I have a few ideas for Sai-jins as a whole.
I know Sai-jins have the ability Kamehameha. Well, I have some new ones.
Lvl. 30 Spirit- Gathered energy ball from evrything.
Yube-ta- More powerful fireball
lvl. 55 Yube-Kamehame\\ha- Most powerful fireball.
Lvl. 80 Galic Gun- Planetary Destruction Beam
Lvl 100 KiKkoken- Ultimate Fireball (can only be used by a Lvl. 4 Super Sai-jin)
Lvl. 1 Store- the ability to store one's power
Once a Say-jin reaches level 100 he/she may begin trabnsofrming into a Super Say-jin.
(The steps for doing this can be similar to becoming an Esper. Except only Sai-jins may do this.)
There are 4 steps. The 1st successful trnasformation lets the lvl. 100 become a lvl. 1 Super Say-jin. This is done until level 4.
Once this is achieved the new S.S. may use the skill KiKkkoken.
<Syntax> KiKkoken  <target>
Say-jin's are also able to use the Store skill whgich lets tyhem increarse thier power in combat.
After you begin to store energy you are  unable to attack until you stop sroing energy. This is done by entering a combat command, like casting a spell, kemehameha etc.

Each round you store you can also take damage, but you also gain a certain + for your abilities or h/d rolls. 
You can store up to X20 fold.
After you reach max of 20 or down to 1 you should immediately stop storing by typing Sstore or type in another command. By typ[ing sstore you immediatel attack with prim weapon.
I thank you for your time.
~
