To      all~
Subject recreation~
Text
I have been getting a lot of tell spam with this question:  "Why did you recreate?"
Since oddly enough several people seem to be interested, I decided to just write a note so whoever else decides to ask me can just read this instead of pestering me.  Enough already.

1) I was starting to collect a lot of valuable items, I.E. tokens, restrings, aqeq, ect. I do not want to risk ketting killed and looted by someone and losing it all.

2) I never fought anyway, most people know that I practically lived at `#K`7a`8ns`7a`#s``, and not through deliberate safe-sitting either, as that is where much of the general RP takes place.

3) I get tired of being pestered to duel when I'm busy by people who don't think that Role-Playing is a real part of this game, and mocked when I refuse.

4) A 13.8k tnl PKer is far too much trouble to level, and unless all the pkers in whatever range I would currently be in would agree not to kill me, I wouldn't ever, by any chance, way, or means, make it to 90.

5) All the Rp points I had been accumulating would be worthless if I couldn't make it to 90. Let's face it, I am just not determined enough to work that hard.

`1R`!u`1k`!a D`1emaris `8[`3MD`#-`3124`8]``
~
