Subject `5C`%o`7u`&n`7c`%i`5l `6N`^e`&ed`^e`6d``~
Text
I haven't played in a `^L`&-`^O`&-`^N`&-`^G`` time and I can tell this MUD is going to shambles.
With Vorlin being the only immortal left who does things to better this mud, we must help as mortals.
Vorlin can code, but does not have access to a shell account for the MUD yet. If he gets one this MUD can live.
This council I am proposing will help keep this MUD as good as it used to be.
I will lead the council (because I thought of it) but we need members from each race/class.
Decide amongest yourselves on good candidates to represent your race or class.
Note me the people you think would be best and I will talk to them.
Sadly, I am more apt to accept a PK set player because the emote command is fine for the RPer's needs.
However, if the person knows a lot about the MUD and knows how each race/class works we need them.
This mud is on a brink of destruction, at the top of a large cliff about to fall.
The MORTALS and Vorlin need to work together to get this back up!
Note me the people who you think know a lot about the MUD/races/classes.
PLEASE do not nominate yourself. Once someone who is on a lot and knows a lot is incharge of your race/class
you can note them your ideas and complaints.
